thread.title: Michelle

author: Michelle
title: Michelle
text:
Snowgoose baskets of cherries and mangoes at Christmas time are always well received and highly rated for quality.
The cherries are not released until they have reached a minimum standard which is preferred to meeting the requested delivery date and sub-optimal product.
When challenged with locations that may not be regularly serviced, the team has been able to provide a workable solution.
Product quality and service are premium.
